'''Lumni-spice''' was the rarest form of [[Spice/Legends|spice]] in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].<ref name="ANB">"[[A New Beginning]]"</ref> It was found on several worlds, usually protected by [[Dragon slug]]s, who consumed it. [[Planet/Legends|Planets]] that boasted the rare fungal growth included [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]<ref name="GG3">''[[Galaxy Guide 3: The Empire Strikes Back]]''</ref> and [[Corulag/Legends|Corulag]].<ref name="Shadow Stalker">{{GalaxyCite|10|Shadow Stalker}}</ref> It was apparently extracted from [[Lumni lichen]].<ref name="ANB" /><ref name="BH:AS">''[[The Bounty Hunters: Aurra Sing]]''</ref>

Shortly before the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] constructed [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] on Hoth, the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Raskar]], lured by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], discovered and attempted to seize a cache of lumni-spice from a deep fissure near the planet's equator, reaching hundreds of meters towards the planet's core. He was chased away by a Dragon Slug.<ref name="ANB" /><ref name="GG3" />

